partnerDetails.about:
REMAX International, Inc. was founded in 1989. The company focused its core
business in providing technology-based products. It gained a reputation of
dependability and extraordinary customer services especially among the banks and
financial institutions. The banking and financial industry became the foremost
customer of REMAX International during the early days of the company’s operation.
